paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_utc2kst_str

cas = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/simple.parquet')\
                .withColumn('datetime', udf_utc2kst_str('datetime'))

df_illum = cas.select('datetime', 'illum').sort('datetime')
df_illum.createOrReplaceTempView('df_illum')

from pyjake.sparkmodule import clean_day_list
from pyspark.sql import Row
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

# cleandays.sort(cleandays.date.desc()).show()

cl = sc.parallelize(clean_day_list).map(lambda d: Row(date=d), StringType()).toDF()
cl.printSchema()
cl.sort(cl.date.desc()).show()
cl.write.mode('overwrite').parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')
